        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Bear River National Heritage Area Study Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of the Interior to conduct a study to assess the suitability and feasibility of designating the study area, including areas in Utah and Idaho that are within the main drainage area of the Bear River, as a National Heritage Area, to be known as the Bear River National Heritage Area. </p>]]>
        </text>
